headline.print_headline: EU Peacekeepers Take Charge at Central African Republic Airport, Violence Rages
headline.main: EU Peacekeepers Take Charge at Central African Republic Airport, Violence Rages

lead_paragraph: European Union peacekeepers took charge of security at Central African Republic's main airport on Wednesday in their first major operation to try and end months of sectarian slaughter.
